<I c="Tutorial" i="tutorial" m="tutorials.tutorial" n="Tutorial_EP17_Rebirth" s="422510">
  <T n="category">422438<!--Tutorial_EP17_Category_Life&Death--></T>
  <T n="name">0xC595D9E2<!--Soul's Journey: Rebirth--></T>
  <L n="slides">
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InEP17\UI\Lessons\EP17_Rebirth_1.png">2f7d0004:00000000:1080ba78a0bdbe9d</T>
      <T n="text">0x7431048<!--Rebirth allows your Sim to start a new life while retaining some pieces of their past. Itâ€™s a unique way to give your Sim a fresh start in the world! Whether you choose to rebirth as a completely new Sim, or a Sim that strongly resembles their past, the choice and story to tell is completely up to you!--></T>
    </U>
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InEP17\UI\Lessons\EP17_Rebirth_2.png">2f7d0004:00000000:1080ba78a0bdbe9e</T>
      <T n="text">0x9DC513A<!--The <b>Burning Soul</b> is a coveted trait given as a reward for completing the last tier of the Soul's Journey, <b>The Big Picture</b>. As a ghost, you can enjoy additional benefits such as being able to use less Ghost Stamina when performing Ghost Mastery abilities!\n\nAfter Rebirth, you will be able to choose one personality trait from your Sim's previous life through the <b>Recall Past Life</b> self-interaction! Additionally, the <b>Peer Into Soul</b> interaction available on mirrors, allows your Sim to recover some other traits acquired from their previous lives. Children, toddler, and infant Sims will also benefit from immediate boosts, with certain Milestones and Developmental Skills unlocked right from the start!--></T>
    </U>
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InEP17\UI\Lessons\EP17_Rebirth_3.png">2f7d0004:00000000:1080ba78a0bdbe9f</T>
      <T n="text">0x8F0BF3F4<!--Reborn Sims also retain certain connections from their previous lives. Your Sim may recognize former family members or Soulmates, gaining special relationship bits that allow them to rebuild familiar bonds. New interactions will give your Sim the chance to rekindle these relationships. These connections help your reborn Sim pick up where they left off, making it easier to reestablish important relationships!--></T>
    </U>
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InEP17\UI\Lessons\EP17_Rebirth_4.png">2f7d0004:00000000:1080ba78a0bdbe98</T>
      <T n="text">0x87CE0761<!--After choosing to Rebirth, whether at the Moment of Death or by visiting Baleful Bog, you will be taken to Manage Worlds to select your new household! The choice is completely up to you, choose to Rebirth into the same family or a completely new one!--></T>
    </U>
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InEP17\UI\Lessons\EP17_Rebirth_5.png">2f7d0004:00000000:1080ba78a0bdbe99</T>
      <T n="text">0x230ED23F<!--Once you've selected a new household and lot to move into, you'll enter Create a Sim to customize your new Sim. The <b>Resemble Past Sim</b> allows you to adjust your Sim's facial structure, skin tone, and eye color to closely match the appearance of the previous Sim. Additionally, <b>Play with Genetics</b> enables you to modify your Sim's look based on the genetics of members from their new household.--></T>
    </U>
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InEP17\UI\Lessons\EP17_Rebirth_6.png">2f7d0004:00000000:1080ba78a0bdbe9a</T>
      <T n="text">0x1D9B8FC9<!--You have the freedom to create and customize any new household members and set applicable relationships to them with your reborn Sim. Certain settings will be restricted such as any romantic relationships. If joining an existing household, existing traits and appearances cannot be modified. Once finished customizing your reborn Sim and additional household members, select Confirm to enter your new household!--></T>
    </U>
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InEP17\UI\Lessons\EP17_Rebirth_7.png">2f7d0004:00000000:1080ba78a0bdbe9b</T>
      <T n="text">0x785CEFEA<!--Now the Rebirth path is complete! Your newly reborn Sim is ready to dive into a fresh start. Check out the Soul's Journey panel to see the Rebirth count, which keeps track of how many times your Sim has been reborn. Progress the Soul's Journey in this new life and unlock the reward to Rebirth again to keep the cycle of new beginnings rolling!--></T>
    </U>
  </L>
